metadata.name: HAMNØY
metadata.description:
Hamnøy, a small fishing village in Norway and this place was in my bucket list for a very long time to shoot.

Fortunately I was able to visit Norway in 2020 before COVID-19 lockdowns. Shooting this village was very tricky as we have to shoot from above a bridge with on going Traffic at night.

Hamnøy is a gorgeous place and witnessing Hamnøy under the Aurora was a marvelous experience.

5330 x 7000 (300DPI)
